Wheeljack-X::

"What in the blue hell ..." Wheeljack trails off as he enters the room 
and sees for himself.  "Ho-kay!  I didn't haul your skidplate in off 
the battlefield just so you could start a demolition derby!"

He fires a pair of magneto-shells to try and short out the berserk 
Maximal's systems.
